GENERAL
=======

Update submodule libuv
----------------------
git submodule add https://github.com/libuv/libuv libuv
cd libuv
git checkout v1.6.1
cd ..
git add libuv
git commit -m 'bumped submodule libuv to version 1.6.1'
git push


LINUX
=====

3rdParty
--------
git clone git://levent.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/levent/libevent
cd libevent; cmake CMakeLists.txt; make; sudo make install

strus & strusAnalyzer
---------------------
For strusRpc to work you have to install strus, strusAnalyzer and strusModule first. 

strusRpc
--------
cmake CMakeLists.txt; make; sudo make install


